# Projects Directory

This directory is mounted to code-server at `/home/coder/workspace`.

Each project should have its own subdirectory here. When editing a project, code-server opens with `?folder=/home/coder/workspace/{project_path}`.

## Structure

```
projects/
├── project-a/
│   ├── src/
│   ├── README.md
│   └── ...
├── project-b/
│   └── ...
└── ...
```

## Note

- Files in this directory are accessible via code-server
- Each project is isolated by its folder parameter
- Do not store sensitive credentials here
